    <h1>NearLink Child Safety Standards</h1>

    <p>NearLink is committed to protecting children and minors and ensuring a safe environment for all users. Our app follows strict safety standards to prevent child sexual abuse and exploitation (CSAE) and other harmful behavior.</p>

    <h2>Age Restrictions</h2>
    <p>Users under the age of 13 are not allowed to create an account on NearLink. Age verification measures are in place to prevent minors from using the app.</p>

    <h2>Monitoring and Reporting</h2>
    <p>All user interactions are monitored to detect and prevent inappropriate content, including content involving child sexual abuse and exploitation. We provide a clear mechanism for reporting abusive behavior or content.</p>

    <h2>How to Report Concerns</h2>
    <p>If you encounter any behavior or content that violates our child safety standards, please contact us immediately:</p>
